IDEA: if you develop buildroot
  Create mirror with all necessary pkgs
    ! Mirrors are the best -- keep old/new/etc versions, dld only necessary !
    ! Don't push your packages into buildroot repo !
  Builds MUST be binary identical
    ! Compare resulting binaries byte to byte
    ! Verify correctness of any upgrade by simple diff
